id":20232,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/27\/hasan-jihad-al-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":19785,"position":1},"title":"Hasan on Jihad: Best jihad is against your soul, desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: It was said to Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cO Abu Sa\u2019id, which jihad is best?\u201d Hasan said, \u201cYour jihad against your desires.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-Muh\u0323ibbi\u0304n 1\/478 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u064a\u0645 \u0648\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0642\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0635\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u0650\u0647\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0636\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062c\u0650\u0647\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064f\u0643\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18878,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/04\/20\/umar-no-killing-civilians\/","url_meta":{"origin":19785,"position":2},"title":"Umar II on War: No killing women, children, civilians, non-combatants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Yahya ibn Yahya reported: I wrote to Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, asking him about the verse, \u201cFight in the way of Allah those who fight you, but do not transgress,\u201d (2:190). Umar wrote back to me, saying, \u201cThis refers to women, children, and whoever\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22406,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/03\/umar-fear-allah-civilians\/","url_meta":{"origin":19785,"position":3},"title":"Umar on War: Fear Allah regarding non-combatants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Wahb reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, decreed, \u201cDo not steal the spoils, do not be treacherous with the enemy, do not mutilate the dead, do not kill children, and fear Allah regarding the farmers who do not wage war against you.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33359,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-umar-why-not-go-for-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":19785,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Ibn Umar, why do you not go for jihad?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Tawus reported: A man said to Abdullah ibn Umar, \u201cWhy do you not join the military campaigns?\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cI heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, say: Verily, Islam is built upon five: to testify there is no God but Allah, to establish prayer,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3657,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/13\/umar-ibn-abdul-aziz-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":19785,"position":5},"title":"Umar II on Faith: Islam is fulfilled by duties, limits, traditions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bukhari reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, faith consists of obligations, laws, limits, and traditions. Whoever perfects them has perfected faith, and whoever does not perfect them will not have perfect faith.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1\/11 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19785","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.co